violin memory inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Hardware
Sub-Industry: Computer Hardware & Storage
Violin Memory, Inc. develops and markets data storage infrastructure products and services. The Company offers products which is used in the areas of database and analytics, metadata servers, scientific computing, and storage caching. Violin Memory operates worldwide.




