			Careers with Violin		










To inquire about career opportunities, please contact us.
      Recruitment Policy
      Violin does not accept unsolicited resumes from any source other than directly from candidates. An unsolicited resume sent to Violin from a recruiter does not constitute any type of relationship between the recruiter and Violin and does not obligate Violin to pay fees if we hire the candidate. All opportunities (with the exception of sales) are based in the Santa Clara, CA headquarters.
      













 









